dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Ralph Lewis. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Ralph. My name is Janice Reed.
Thank you, Janice. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six eight two one and my date of birth is zero seven one nine eight five.
Great, thank you for providing that information, Janice. Can you also share with me your current vehicle make and model?
Of course, I drive a two zero one nine Ford Escape.
Thank you, Janice. Is there anything specific you would like to discuss or inquire about regarding your insurance policy today?
I just wanted to inquire about adding roadside assistance to my policy.
I can assist you with that. Let me provide you with the details on how to add that coverage. Thank you for reaching out, Janice. Have a great day!
Thank you, Ralph. You've been very helpful. Farewell.
